0. Init Rails and Install HAML (see http://haml.hamptoncatlin.com/download)

rails your_survey_app
cd your_survey_app
mv public/index.html public/index.html.old

gem install --no-ri haml
haml --rails .

1. Install Rails Engines Plugin (see http://rails-engines.org/download)

ruby script/plugin install git://github.com/lazyatom/engines.git

2. Install SurveyOR (surveys on rails)

ruby script/plugin install git://github.com/breakpointer/surveyor.git

or using git submodule (if want the bleeding edge, see http://www.kernel.org/pub/software/scm/git/docs/git-submodule.html)

git submodule add git://github.com/breakpointer/surveyor.git vendor/plugins/surveyor
git submodule init
git submodule update

3. Setup SurveyOR

In config/environment.rb... after require File.join(File.dirname(__FILE__), 'boot') add:
  require File.join(File.dirname(__FILE__), '../vendor/plugins/engines/boot')

In config/routes.rb add:
  map.from_plugin :surveyor

Run:
  script/generate plugin_migration && rake db:migrate
  
  